{"tid":1927911,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"有美國公民向美法院提集體訴訟 控告中国政府隱瞞疫情 導致全球蔓延 造成損失","createTime":"2020-03-16T05:30:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-16T14:00:10.000Z","uid":48083,"like":168,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"d7707887325606454e1d646656615587a0e4782b","tid":1927911,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T05:30:45.000Z","msg":"【2020年03月16日】（歐洲希望之聲記者鄭平報導）中共在武漢肺炎爆發初期隱瞞疫情，不僅令疫情在中國境內擴散，而且殃及全球。3月13日，4名美國人及1家公司於聯名向美國佛羅里達州南區地區法院邁阿密分院提起一項針對中國政府及其相關部門的集體訴訟。<br />\n<br />\n綜合美媒消息，被告機構包括：中國政府（People&rsquo;s Republic of China）、中共國家健康衛生委員會、應急管理部、民政部、湖北省與武漢市政府。<br />\n<br />\n起訴書指，中國（中共）政府及其他被告為維護經濟利益和超級大國地位，瞞報病情，導致疫情在全球的蔓延，並對五名原告造成了損害。<br />\n<br />\n原告包括4名佛羅里達州居民，及位於佛州棕櫚灘縣的一家棒球運動員培訓中心。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://sohfrance.org/wuhanfeiyankaishilemeiguo5yuangaolianshoujiangzhongguozhengfugaoshangfating/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsohfrance.org%2Fwuhanfeiyankaishilemeiguo5yuangaolianshoujiangzhongguozhengfugaoshangfating%2F&d=ly5XvLwGuIZ6JSW2uqe%2Bvo5RPfZ%2FgKFUZzIsJfjgB6g%3D&h=4032cfeb\" target=\"_blank\">https://sohfrance.org/wuhanfeiyankaishilemeiguo5yuangaolianshoujiangzhongguozhengfugaoshangfating/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nClass Action Filed Against China Over COVID-19 Outbreak<br />\n<br />\nThe suit, filed Thursday, alleges Chinese authorities &quot;proverbially put their head in the sand&quot; for their own economic self interest, sparking the global COVID-19 outbreak.<br />\n<br />\nBy Amanda Bronstad  三月 13, 2020 at 04:23 下午<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.law.com/dailybusinessreview/2020/03/13/class-action-filed-against-china-over-covid-19-outbreak/?slreturn=20200216012144\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.law.com%2Fdailybusinessreview%2F2020%2F03%2F13%2Fclass-action-filed-against-china-over-covid-19-outbreak%2F%3Fslreturn%3D20200216012144&d=ly5XvLwGuIZ6JSW2uqe%2Bvo5RPfZ%2FgKFUZzIsJfjgB6g%3D&h=a8d0313b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.law.com/dailybusinessreview/2020/03/13/class-action-filed-against-china-over-covid-19-outbreak/?slreturn=20200216012144</a>"},{"pid":"c2b12b4821ba879380185409f71e289f7f6e6811","tid":1927911,"uid":279779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T05:32:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"891f5b1e1c4b002b5732bbd89c0a4330826eeedd","tid":1927911,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T05:32:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b23a653ae8808dc446dcd03369cb5121916582bd","tid":1927911,"uid":134415,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T05:33:26.000Z","msg":"鹹濕蔡: 世人應當感恩"},{"pid":"9d03e93497868e7798eb52057a681d5dbe3728bc","tid":1927911,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T05:33:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec9d30b6f776295c7dcde87ce6cec66895ca414f","tid":1927911,"uid":48083,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T05:34:33.000Z","msg":"話時話<br />\n係咪美國人先有得join<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"906133cde6aa1b14b1de28c43c4691610f8c42ba","tid":1927911,"uid":7369,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T05:34:48.000Z","msg":"加油呀"},{"pid":"5e62297b673ec15783c232f3ba8dc45f91b71c09","tid":1927911,"uid":48083,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T05:35:11.000Z","msg":"該律師行表示，自從提交起訴書以來，已經收到了幾十人的電話要求把他們也追加為共同原告。"},{"p